                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000709-27-off134 t18000709-27-cd135"></join>, a hammer, value 6d. a chissel, value 4d. a hollow plane value 1s. a chalk line, value 1d. a long plane, value 2s. a jack plane, value 2s. and a smoothing-plane, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000709-27-victim244" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Scott
                  <interp inst="t18000709-27-victim244" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
