                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000709-27-off134 t18000709-27-crimeloc136"></join>, I am a <rs id="t18000709-27-viclabel137" type="occupation">journeyman carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000709-27-victim244 t18000709-27-viclabel137"></join>: On the 8th of May, I missed my tools from a building where I was at work near Waltham-cross-turnpike, at Mr. Kent's house; I left my tools there on the evening of the 7th.</p>
               <p>Q.Look at these tools? - A. They are mine.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know any thing of the prisoner? - A. No.</p>


               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am innocent of it, I never had these tools in my possession.</p>
